@Tadas As said in my last comment https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/pull/17227#discussion_r908736348, I prefer `[Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.ExportPSSessionCommand, Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.Utility]` as in
```c#
Type type = typeof(ExportPSSessionCommand);
string asmName = type.Assembly.GetName().Name;
string versionOfScriptGenerator = $"[{type.FullName}, {asmName}]::VersionOfScriptGenerator";
```
But this is not a blocking comment, so it's up to @PaulHigin to decide if merging this PR as is.
